"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_hand_of_midas_lua_Description"  "<h1>Active: Transmute</h1> Instantly destroys a non-hero unit, granting %bonus_gold% gold and %xp_multiplier%× experience. When used on a neutral creep before Round %drop_end%, guarantees to drop a neutral item token if eligible."
