"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_smoke_of_deceit_lua"       "SMOKE OF CHAOS"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_smoke_of_deceit_lua_Description"  "<h1>Active: Stealth</h1> Renders the caster and nearby allied player‑controlled units within %application_radius% radius invisible for %duration% seconds, and grants them %bonus_movement_speed%%% bonus movement speed. Their icons are also hidden from the minimap.<br><br>Neither attacking nor casting spells will break this invisibility. It is only dispelled when approaching within %visibility_radius% range of an enemy hero.<br><br>Stealth‑granted invisibility cannot be revealed by True Sight."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_smoke_of_deceit_lua"                              "SMOKE OF CHAOS"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_smoke_of_deceit_lua_Description"            "Invisibility: Movement speed increased. Stealth is only broken when approaching an enemy hero within range."

