"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_greater_mango_lua"	"DELICIOUS MANGO!"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_greater_mango_lua_Description"	"<h1>Active: Devour Delicious Mango!</h1>Reduce your current health to %hp%, and become unable to heal or regenerate health for %duration% seconds. This duration does not tick down while in the Fountain. Does not cost any ability points. Instantly learn all of your talents, regardless of level requirements.<br><br>Cannot be used while in the Fountain."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_greater_mango_lua"		"DELICIOUS!"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_greater_mango_lua_Description"	"Cannot restore health or be healed."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_1"       "WOLF CAPE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_1_Description"    "<h1>Passive: Battlefield Triage</h1> Attacking a neutral creep grants a shield that absorbs physical damage from neutrals equal to %shield_hp_pct%%% of the attack damage, up to %max_shield_hp% per hit, lasting %shield_duration% seconds.<br><br>Maximum shield capacity is %max_hp_pct%%% of your hero's maximum health.\n<h1>Passive: Tactician</h1> Attacks have a %buff_chance%%% chance to apply a buff that reduces damage taken from neutral creeps by %creep_damage_reduce%%% for %buff_duration% seconds."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_shield"		"BATTLEFIELD TRIAGE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_shield_Description"	"Grants a shield that blocks %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP% damage from neutral creeps."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_buff"		"TACTICIAN"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_buff_Description"	"Damage taken from neutral creeps is reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_2"       "UNFINISHED HEARTGUARD"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_2_Description"  "<h1>Passive: Battlefield Triage</h1> Attacks against neutral creeps grant a shield that blocks physical damage from neutrals equal to %shield_hp_pct%%% of the attack damage dealt (up to %max_shield_hp% per hit), lasting %shield_duration% seconds.<br><br>Maximum total shield value is limited to %max_hp_pct%%% of your hero's maximum health.\n<h1>Passive: Tactician</h1> Attacks have a %buff_chance%%% chance to grant a buff that reduces damage taken from neutral creeps by %creep_damage_reduce%%% for %buff_duration% seconds."
// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_2_all_stats"   "+$all"
