"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_2_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_2_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_2_Lore"       "A legendary craftsman created the prototype of this artifact, but struggled with how to continue its refinement."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3"	"KOI'S HEARTGUARD"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_Description"	"<h1>Active: Suppress</h1> Targets all visible enemy units within %abilitycastrange% range, slowing their movement speed.<br>Simultaneously applies a basic dispel to self, granting increased movement speed and slow immunity for %purge_slow_duration% seconds.<br><br>If the target is a non-hero unit, also roots it for %purge_root_duration% seconds.<br><br>Both the movement speed slow and increase start at 100%% and gradually decay to 0%% over the buff duration.\n\n<h1>Passive: Spellbreak</h1> Each attack burns %feedback_mana_burn% mana from the target and deals %damage_per_burn% physical damage per point of mana burned.\n<h1>Passive: Battlefield Triage</h1> Attacks against neutral creeps grant a shield that absorbs physical damage from neutrals equal to %shield_hp_pct%%% of the attack damage dealt (up to %max_shield_hp% per hit), lasting %shield_duration% seconds.<br><br>Maximum total shield value is %max_hp_base% + %max_hp_pct%%% of the caster's maximum health.\n<h1>Passive: Tactician</h1> Attacks have a %buff_chance%%% chance to grant a buff that reduces damage taken from neutral creeps by %creep_damage_reduce%%% for %buff_duration% seconds."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_felling_shield_lua_3_Lore"   "A warrior named Koi brought a precious piece of stone. Two months later, the Heartguard was finally completed."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_slow"		"SUPPRESS"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_felling_shield_lua_3_slow_Description"	"Movement speed reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%."
