"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff"	"NH'S WAND"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff_manacost_reduction"	"%+$manacost_reduction"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Arcane Overload</h1> Magic damage has a %magic_crit_pct%%% chance to critically strike for %magic_crit_damage%%% damage.<br><br>Does not affect percentage-based damage."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_noob_staff_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>A wand imbued with the arcane energies of ancient times.</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen"	"FALLEN ONE‘S SKULL"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_all_stats"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_bonus_hp_regen"	"+$hp_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Description"	"<h1>Active: Legion's Descent</h1>The Fel Domination Aura provides Spell Immunity and True Strike, lasting for %duration% seconds.<br><br>Cannot be refreshed.\n<h1>Passive: Fel Domination</h1>Provides nearby allies with %life_steal_pct%%% life steal, %bonus_movespeed% movement speed, %bonus_attack_speed% attack speed, %spell_amp%%% spell amplification, %magical_resistance%%% magic resistance, and %evasion%%% evasion, while surrounding allies with Fel Flames. Every %burn_interval% seconds, enemies within a %burn_radius% radius take %burn_damage% magic damage. Fel Flames can stack.<br><br>The effect is multiplied by %creep_mult%%% for non-hero allies.<br><br>Radius: %radius%"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>We answered the call, but at what cost?</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_effect"		"FEL DOMINATION"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_effect_Description"	"Grants %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%% Lifesteal, %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT% Movement Speed, %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT% Attack Speed, %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_SPELL_AMPLIFY_PERCENTAGE%%% Spell Amplification, %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MAGICAL_RESISTANCE_BONUS%%% Magic Resistance, and %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_EVASION_CONSTANT%%% Evasion, while continuously scorching nearby enemies."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Active"		"LEGION‘S DESCENT"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_Active_Description"	"The Fel Domination Aura provides Spell Immunity and True Strike."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_burn"		"FEL FLAMES"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_Head_of_the_Fallen_burn_Description"	"Your soul shall be tormented!"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff"	"STARGAZER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_manacost_reduction"	"%+$manacost_reduction"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_all_stats"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_Description"	"<h1>Active: Manaflare</h1>Unleashes a wave of weakening energy, increasing magic damage taken by enemies within %debuff_radius% by %bonus_magical_dmg%%%.<br><br>Cast Range: %abilitycastrange%<br>Duration: %debuff_duration% seconds.\n<h1>Passive: Prismatic Barrier</h1> Whenever you deal critical magic damage, you gain a buff that reduces damage taken from neutral creeps by %creep_damage_reduce%%% for %buff_duration% seconds.\n<h1>Passive: Arcane Surge</h1> Magic damage has a %magic_crit_pct%%% chance to critically strike for %magic_crit_damage%%% damage.<br><br>Cooldown: %crit_cd% seconds (affected by cooldown reduction). No cooldown when attacking neutral creeps affected by Manaflare.<br><br>Does not affect percentage-based damage."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_stargazing_staff_Lore"	"A staff made of meteorite."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_cd"		"ARCANE SURGE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_cd_Description"	"Arcane Surge is on cooldown."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_buff"		"PRISMATIC BARRIER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_buff_Description"	"Damage taken from neutral creeps is reduced by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_INCOMING_DAMAGE_PERCENTAGE%%%."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_debuff"	"MANAFLARE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_stargazing_staff_debuff_Description"	"Increases magic damage taken by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>KAST, GREATSTAFF OF THE MAGNA</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_manacost_reduction"	"%+$manacost_reduction"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_Description"	"<h1>Active: Manaflare</h1>Releases a wave of debilitating energy that roots enemies within a %debuff_radius% radius for %root_duration% seconds and increases magic damage they take by %bonus_magical_dmg%%% for %debuff_duration% seconds.<br><br>If the target is a non-hero unit, it also loses all mana for the duration of the root, restoring it once the effect ends.<br><br>Cast Range: %abilitycastrange%\n<h1>Passive: Prismatic Barrier</h1> Whenever you deal critical magic damage, you gain a buff that reduces damage taken from neutral creeps by %creep_damage_reduce%%% for %buff_duration% seconds.\n<h1>Passive: Arcane Surge</h1> Magic damage has a %magic_crit_pct%%% chance to critically strike for %magic_crit_damage%%% damage.<br><br>Cooldown: %crit_cd% seconds. No cooldown when attacking neutral creeps affected by Manaflare, and the critical strike chance is increased by an additional %bonus_magic_cirt_pct%%% against such targets.<br><br>Does not affect percentage-based damage."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_aluneth_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>To safeguard the supreme interests of the Arcane Council, several of its most powerful Guardians poured nearly all of their power into this staff.</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_aluneth_root"	"MANAFLARE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_aluneth_root_Description"	"Ensnared."

