"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon"	"<font color='#ff8000'>Lunar Temple Longbow</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_bonus_attack_range"	"+$attack_range"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_projectile_speed"	"+$projectile_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Lunar Barrage</h1> Each attack fires a barrage of %arrow_count% Lunar Arrows. Each arrow deals magic damage equal to %arrow_dmg_pct%%% of your attack damage. Damage increases with distance, and enemies hit are knocked back up to %max_knockback_distance% units.<br><br>Enemies cannot be knocked back outside your attack range.<br><br>Damage bonus per unit of distance: %arrow_bonus_dmg_per_range%%%.\n<h1>Passive: Sharpshooter‘s Focus</h1> When equipped by a ranged hero, grants %bonus_range_per_stat% attack range per point of primary attribute."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_wild_moon_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>The energy of the Moonwell flows through the bow‘s frame.</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller"	"<font color='#ff8000'>Stormreaver's Thunderblade</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_evasion"	"+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Dancing Lightning</h1>Upon hitting an enemy with an attack, unleash a bouncing lightning bolt that strikes %jump_count% enemies. The lightning deals damage equal to %damage_pct%%% of your attack damage. Enemies hit by the lightning become <font color='#69b7f2'>Electrified</font> for %slow_duration% seconds.<br><br><font color='#69b7f2'>Electrified</font> enemies take %bonus_damage_pct%%% increased physical damage, have their attack speed reduced by %attack_slow%, cast speed reduced by %cast_slow%%%, and cannot benefit from True Strike.\n<h1>Passive: Thunderstorm</h1>Attacks and Dancing Lightning have a %crit_chance%%% chance to deal %crit_damage%%% critical strike damage.\n<h1>Passive: Windborne</h1>Grants %bonus_movespeed%%% bonus movement speed. When equipped by a melee hero, also grants %bonus_attack_speed_pct%%% bonus attack speed."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thunder_caller_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>Awaken, Fury of the Thunder!</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_thunder_caller_debuff"	"<font color='#69b7f2'>Electrified</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_thunder_caller_debuff_Description"	"+%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_INCOMING_PHYSICAL_DAMAGE_PERCENTAGE%%% Physical Damage Taken, -%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT% AS, -%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_CASTTIME_PERCENTAGE%%% Cast Speed, No True Strike."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul"	"<font color='#ff8000'>Rizzrack's Soulstaff</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_Description"	"<h1>Active: Infinite Power</h1>For %duration% seconds, you become immune to silence and gain the following effects: reduced cast point by %casttime_reduction%%%, increased mana cost by %bonus_manacost%%%, increased cast range by %bonus_cast_range%, and reduced cooldowns by %cooldown_reduction%%% (with a minimum cooldown of %cooldown_min% seconds).<br><br>Cannot be refreshed.<br>Does not affect Refresher Orb‘s cooldown.\n<h1>Passive: Arcane Mastery</h1> Grants bonus mana regeneration. This effect is significantly amplified as your current mana decreases."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_ryze_soul_Lore"	"<font color='#f7ab00'>In the end, this powerful rune mage chose this very staff to be the final vessel for his soul.</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_ryze_soul_buff"	"INFINITE POWER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_ryze_soul_buff_Description"	"Indiscriminate bombardment!"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_moon_shard"		"DARKMOON SHARD"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_moon_shard_Description"	"<h1>Active: Consume</h1> Consume the Darkmoon Shard to permanently reduce your base attack time by %base_attack_time_reduction%% (to a minimum of %base_attack_time_min%). Can only be used once."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_moon_shard_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_moon_shard"	"DARKMOON SHARD"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_moon_shard_Description"	"Base attack time reduced to %fMODIFIER_PROPERTY_BASE_ATTACK_TIME_CONSTANT%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song"	"<font color='#c600ff'>Azure Sky Melody</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_health"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_bonus_spell_amp"	"%+$spell_amp"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_mana_regen_multiplier"	"%+Mana Regeneration Amplification"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_spell_lifesteal_amp"	"%+Spell Lifesteal Amplification"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Spell Empowerment</h1> Your next damaging spell or item will deal an additional %bonus_dmg% magic damage to the primary target and all enemies within a %radius% radius, and slow them by %movement_slow%%% for %slow_duration% seconds.<br><br>Passive abilities cannot trigger this effect.\n<h1>Passive: Mango Might!</h1> Grants %spell_amp_per_int%%% Spell Amplification per point of Intelligence, and %spell_amp_per_other%%% per point of Strength or Agility.<br><br>Effect is reduced to %hero_pct%%% when targeting heroes.<br><br>Does not affect percentage-based damage.\n<h1>Unique:</h1> This item is unique. Its attributes and effects do not stack."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_azure_song_Lore"	"A longsword brimming with arcane energy, the object of desire for countless mages of that era."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song_slow"	"SPELL EMPOWERMENT"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song_slow_Description"	"Movement speed slowed by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%%."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>Star Chart</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_azure_song_Description"	"<font color='#B694FF'>Total Spell Amplification</font> increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>Star Chart</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_health"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_bonus_spell_amp"	"%+$spell_amp"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_mana_regen_multiplier"	"%+Mana Regeneration Amplification"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_spell_lifesteal_amp"	"%+Spell Lifesteal Amplification"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Spell Empowerment</h1> Your next damaging spell or item will deal an additional %bonus_dmg% magic damage to the primary target and all enemies within a %radius% radius, and slow them by %movement_slow%%% for %slow_duration% seconds.<br><br>Passive abilities cannot trigger this effect.\n<h1>Passive: Mango Might!</h1> Grants %spell_amp_per_int%%% Spell Amplification per point of Intelligence, and %spell_amp_per_other%%% per point of Strength or Agility.<br><br>Effect is reduced to %hero_pct%%% when targeting heroes.<br><br>Does not affect percentage-based damage.\n<h1>Passive: Firmament's Grand Design</h1> During the day, for every %total_spell_amp_threshold% charges this item holds, your <font color='#B694FF'>Total Spell Amplification</font> is increased by %total_spell_amp_pct_day%%%.<br><br>At night, for every %total_spell_amp_threshold% charges this item holds, your <font color='#B694FF'>Total Spell Amplification</font> is increased by %total_spell_amp_pct_night%%%.\n<h1>Unique:</h1> This item is unique. Its attributes and effects do not stack."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_star_design_Lore"	"<font color='#B694FF'>In all the heavens and earth, only the arcane reigns supreme.</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker"	"ARCANE WALKER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_mana_pct"	"%+$max_mana_percentage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_bonus_movement"	"+$move_speed"
// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_mana_regen_multiplier"	"%+魔法恢复增强"
// "DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_spell_lifesteal_amp"	"%+技能吸血增强"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_Description"	"<h1>Active: Mana Infusion</h1> Restores %replenish_amount% mana to the hero.<br><br>For every %one_pct_tooltip%%% of maximum mana missing, the amount restored is increased by %bonus_replenish_amount_pct%%%.\n<h1>Passive: Aether Focus</h1> Increases the cast range of targeted spells and items by %cast_range_bonus%.\n<h1>Passive: Spellpiercer</h1> Grants %magical_armor_pen%%% <font color='#B694FF'>Magic Penetration</font>.<br><br>Starts with %initial_charge% charges.<br>Gain %kill_charge% charge per enemy hero kill, up to a maximum of %max_charge%.<br>Each %one_pct_tooltip% charge provides %magical_armor_pen_pct_charge%%% <font color='#B694FF'>Percentage Magic Penetration</font>. When targeting heroes, each charge also grants %spell_amp_charge%%% Spell Amplification.<br>Lose %death_lose_charge% charges upon death to an enemy hero.<br><br>Does not affect percentage-based damage.\n<h1>Unique:</h1> This item is unique. Movement speed bonuses from multiple boots do not stack, and its attributes and effects are not stackable."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_arcane_walker_Lore"	"Since it's boots for mages, you can also call them: \"Spell Pierce Boots\""
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_arcane_walker_magical_armor_pen"	"MAGIC PENETRATION"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_arcane_walker_magical_armor_pen_Description"	"Treated as having only %fMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%% Magic Resistance."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter"	"GANG LETTER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_str"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_letter_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Legion Aura</h1> Empowers your controlled non-hero units, granting them:<br>• **Per 1 Attribute:** %aura_bonus_damage_str%%% Base Attack Damage<br>• **Per 1 Strength:** %aura_bonus_hp_str%%% Max Health and deals %aura_bonus_return_str% Physical Damage to attackers (cooldown: %aura_bonus_return_str_cd% seconds)<br>• **Per 1 Agility:** %aura_bonus_armor_agi% Armor and %aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi% Attack Speed<br>• **Attacks** deal an additional %aura_bonus_magical_damage_int% Magic Damage<br>• **Per 1 Intelligence:** %aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%% Spell Amplification and %aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%% Magic Resistance<br><br>Aura Radius: %aura_radius%\n<h1>Unique & Boot-Class Item:</h1> • This item is unique. Its attributes and effects do not stack.<br> • If multiple [Letter] items are equipped, only the last one applies.<br> • This item is classified as Boots. Movement speed bonuses from multiple boots do not stack."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_letter_effect"	"LEGION AURA"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_letter_effect_Description"	"Attack increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_BASEDAMAGEOUTGOING_PERCENTAGE%%%, Health increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_EXTRA_HEALTH_PERCENTAGE%%%, Attack Speed increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%, Armor increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS%, Spell Damage increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_SPELL_AMPLIFY_PERCENTAGE%%%, and Magical Resistance increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MAGICAL_RESISTANCE_BONUS%%%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter"	"GANG EXECUTIVE LETTER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_str"	"+$all"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_senior_letter_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Legion Aura</h1> Empowers your controlled non-hero units, granting them:<br>• **Per Attribute:** %aura_bonus_damage_str%%% Base Attack Damage<br>• **Per Strength:** %aura_bonus_hp_str%%% Max Health and deals %aura_bonus_return_str% Physical Damage to attackers (cooldown: %aura_bonus_return_str_cd% seconds)<br>• **Per Agility:** %aura_bonus_armor_agi% Armor and %aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi% Attack Speed<br>• **Attacks** also deal an additional %aura_bonus_magical_damage_int% Magic Damage<br>• **Per Intelligence:** %aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%% Spell Amplification and %aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%% Magic Resistance<br><br>Aura Radius: %aura_radius%\n<h1>Unique & Boot-Class Item:</h1> • This item is unique. Its attributes and effects do not stack.<br> • If multiple [Letter] items are equipped, only the last one applies.<br> • This item is classified as Boots. Movement speed bonuses from multiple boots do not stack."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter"	"GANG GHOST STORIES"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_spell_amp"	"%+$spell_amp"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_ghost_letter_Description"	"<h1>Active: Soulshoe Hunt</h1>Grants True Strike to allies under the influence of Gang Aura for %duration% seconds, without changing the type of damage dealt by their attacks.<br><br>Allows attacks on ethereal units, dealing additional %damage_pct%%% of attack as Magical Damage.<br><br>Also: Shares your %bonus_spell_amp_active%%% Spell Amplification with the units you summon.<br><br>Area of Effect: %aura_radius%\n<h1>Passive: Gang Aura</h1>Enhances your controlled creeps, granting them:<br>For every 1 attribute, gain %aura_bonus_damage_str%%% Base Damage<br>For every 1 Strength, gain %aura_bonus_hp_str%%% max Health and deal %aura_bonus_return_str% Physical Damage to attackers (Cooldown: %aura_bonus_return_str_cd% seconds)<br>For every 1 Agility, gain %aura_bonus_armor_agi% Armor and %aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi% Attack Speed<br>Deals an additional %aura_bonus_magical_damage_int% Magical Damage, and for every 1 Intelligence, gain %aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%% Spell Damage and %aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%% Magical Resistance.<br><br>Also: +%aura_spell_amp_constant%%% Spell Damage, +%aura_projectile_speed% Projectile Speed<br><br>Area of Effect: %aura_radius%\nThis item is unique; all its attributes and effects are not stackable. If multiple items are equipped, only the last one will take effect.\nThis item is considered a pair of boots, and Movement Speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_ghost_letter"	"SOULSHOE HUNT"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_ghost_letter_Description"	"Grants True Strike and allows attacks to hit Ethereal units."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter"	"GANG MEAL VOUCHER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_bonus_hp_regen_pct"	"%+Max Health Regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_dinner_invitation_letter_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Eat Up!</h1>Redirects %link_damage%%% of the damage you take to an ally under the influence of Gang Aura, prioritizing the unit with the highest health.\n<h1>Passive: Gang Aura</h1>Enhances your controlled creeps, granting them:<br>For every 1 attributes, gain %aura_bonus_damage_str%%% Base Damage<br>For every 1 Strength, gain %aura_bonus_hp_str%%% max Health and deal %aura_bonus_return_str% Physical Damage to attackers(cooldown:%aura_bonus_return_str_cd% second)<br>For every 1 Agility, gain %aura_bonus_armor_agi% Armor and %aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi% Attack Speed<br>Deals an additional %aura_bonus_magical_damage_int% Magical Damage, and for every 1 Intelligence, gain %aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%% Spell Damage and %aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%Magical Resistance<br>Also:+%aura_hp_regen_pct%%% Max Health Regeneration, +%aura_lifesteal%%% Shared Lifesteal (Effectiveness against wards is reduced by %aura_lifesteal_other%%%), +%aura_bonus_damage_pct%%% Bonus Damage, +%aura_bonus_armor% Armor<br><br>Area of Effect: %aura_radius%\nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable. If multiple letters are equipped, only the last one will take effect.\nThis item is considered a pair of boots; Movement Speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet"	"GANG CHALLENGE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_gauntlet_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Street Brawl</h1>Allies under the influence of Gang Aura have a %aura_accuracy_chance%%% chance to ignore evasion with each attack, and a %aura_bash_chance%%% chance to stun the target for %aura_bash_duration% seconds. No cooldown when targeting a neutral creep. \n<h1>Passive: Gang Aura</h1>Enhances your controlled creeps, granting them:<br>For every 1 attributes, gain %aura_bonus_damage_str%%% Base Damage<br>For every 1 Strength, gain %aura_bonus_hp_str%%% max Health and deal %aura_bonus_return_str% Physical Damage to attackers(cooldown:%aura_bonus_return_str_cd% second)<br>For every 1 Agility, gain %aura_bonus_armor_agi% Armor and %aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi% Attack Speed<br>Deals an additional %aura_bonus_magical_damage_int% Magical Damage, and for every 1 Intelligence, gain %aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%% Spell Damage and %aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%Magical Resistance<br><br>Area of Effect: %aura_radius%\nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable. If multiple letters are equipped, only the last one will take effect.\nThis item is considered a pair of boots; Movement Speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket"	"GANG PLANE TICKET"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_gang_plane_ticket_Description"	"<h1>Active: Paratrooper Drop</h1>Teleports allies under the influence of Gang Aura to the farthest location within a range of %abilitycastrange%, and induces fear in enemies for %duration% seconds.<br>Area of Effect: %blink_radius%\n<h1>Passive: Gang Aura</h1>Enhances your controlled creeps, granting them:<br>For every 1 attributes, gain %aura_bonus_damage_str%%% Base Damage<br>For every 1 Strength, gain %aura_bonus_hp_str%%% max Health and deal %aura_bonus_return_str% Physical Damage to attackers(cooldown:%aura_bonus_return_str_cd% second)<br>For every 1 Agility, gain %aura_bonus_armor_agi% Armor and %aura_bonus_attackspeed_agi% Attack Speed<br>Deals an additional %aura_bonus_magical_damage_int% Magical Damage, and for every 1 Intelligence, gain %aura_bonus_spell_amp_int%%% Spell Damage and %aura_bonus_magical_resist_int%%%Magical Resistance<br>Also:+%aura_attack_range% Attack Range<font color='#7d7d7d'>(Ranged Only)</font>, +%aura_attack_range_melee%<font color='#7d7d7d'>(Melee Only)</font>, A %aura_crit_chance%%% chance to deal %aura_crit_damage%%% damage with each attack.<br>If attacking an enemy applied by Fear, guarantees dealing %aura_crit_damage%%% damage.<br><br>Area of Effect: %aura_radius%\nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable. If multiple letters are equipped, only the last one will take effect.\nThis item is considered a pair of boots; Movement Speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_plane_ticket"	"Gotcha!"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_gang_plane_ticket_Description"	"Run!"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots"	"BLOODSTONE BOOTS"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_int"	"+$int"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_str"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_hp"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_mana_pct"	"%+$max_mana_percentage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_mana_regen"	"+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_movement"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_bonus_spell_lifesteal"	"%+$spell_lifesteal"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_Description"	"<h1>Active: Bloodstone Pact</h1>Restores %replenish_amount% mana to the hero.<br><br>For each %one_pct_tooltip%%% missing mana, the mana restored is increased by %bonus_replenish_amount_pct%%%.<br><br>Increases Bloodstone Boots' Spell Lifesteal by %lifesteal_multiplier%x and converts the same percentage of damage dealt to mana. Lasts %duration% seconds.\n<h1>Passive: Aether Focus</h1>Increases cast range of targeted abilities and items by %cast_range_bonus%.\n<h1>Passive: Magic Pierce</h1>
Grants %magical_armor_pen%%% <font color='#B694FF'>Spell Penetration</font>.<br><br>Starts with %initial_charge% energy.<br>Gain %kill_charge% energy per enemy hero kill, up to %max_charge% energy.<br>Every %one_pct_tooltip% energy grants %magical_armor_pen_pct_charge%%% <font color='#B694FF'>Spell Penetration</font>, %spell_lifesteal_charge%%% Spell Lifesteal, and %spell_amp_charge%%% Spell Amplification against heroes.<br>Lose %death_lose_charge% energy when killed by an enemy hero.<br><br>
Percentage-based abilities are disabled.<br><br>\nMovement speed bonuses from multiple boots do not stack.<br>\nThis item is unique and its effects do not stack."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blood_boots_Lore"	"Made by Hex Technology."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_blood_boots"	"BLOODSTONE PACT"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_blood_boots_Description"	"Bloodstone Boots' Spell Lifesteal increased."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh"	"<font color='#c600ff'>Last Laugh</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_health_regen"   "+$hp_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_mana_regen"   "+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_attack_range"	"+$attack_range"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_bonus_attack_range_melee"	"+$attack_range_melee"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Description"	"<h1>Active: Phase</h1>Gives %phase_movement_speed%%% increased movement speed, lets you move through units and trees, and turn more quickly for %phase_duration% seconds. \n<h1>Passive: Quell</h1>Total attack damage increased by %quelling_bonus%%%.<br><br>Attacking player-controlled units will weaken this effect by %hero_pct_reduction%%% for %disable_duration% seconds. \n<h1>Passive: Cleave</h1>Melee/Ranged heroes deal %cleave_damage_percent%%%/%cleave_damage_percent_ranged%%% of attack damage as physical damage in a cone up to %cleave_distance%/%cleave_distance_ranged% around the target. \nMovement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack. \nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Note0"	"Cleave damage goes through spell immunity."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Note1"	"If multiple sources of Cleave are present, each Cleave's damage is applied separately."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh"	"CRITICAL STRIKE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_Description"	"Critical Strike chance increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%%%, damage increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP2%%%"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_active"	"PHASE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_active_Description"	"Movement speed increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_MOVESPEED_BONUS_PERCENTAGE%%% and allows you to move through units."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_last_laugh_disable"	"SHOW MERCY"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_last_laugh_Lore"	"The bearer of this mighty axe gains the ability to cut down swaths of enemies at once."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>FLAME REAPER</font>"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_health_regen"   "+$hp_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_mana_regen"   "+$mana_regen"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_movement_speed"	"+$move_speed"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_attack_range"	"+$attack_range"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_bonus_attack_range_melee"	"+$attack_range_melee"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Description"	"<h1>Active: Phase</h1>Gives %phase_movement_speed%%% increased movement speed, lets you move through units and trees, and turn more quickly for %phase_duration% seconds. \n<h1>Passive: Quell</h1>Total attack damage increased by %quelling_bonus%%%.<br><br>Attacking player-controlled units will weaken this effect by %hero_pct_reduction%%% for %disable_duration% seconds. \n<h1>Passive: Cleave</h1>Melee/Ranged heroes deal %cleave_damage_percent%%%/%cleave_damage_percent_ranged%%% of attack damage as physical damage in a cone up to %cleave_distance%/%cleave_distance_ranged% around the target. \n<h1>Passive: Critical Strike</h1>Grants each attack a %crit_chance%%% chance to deal %crit_multiplier%%% damage. \nMovement speed bonuses from multiple pairs of boots do not stack. \nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Note0"	"Cleave damage goes through spell immunity."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Note1"	"If multiple sources of Cleave are present, each Cleave's damage is applied separately."
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_flame_reaper_Lore"	"<font color='#e5cc80'>One Hit</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor"	"LACERATE CLOUD"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_cloud_razor_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Lacerate</h1>Physical damage reduces the target's armor by %corruption_armor% for %corruption_duration% seconds.<br><br>Start with %initial_charge% energy points.<br>Gain %kill_charge% energy points for each enemy hero kill, up to a maximum of %max_charge% points.<br>Every %one_pct_tooltip% energy points grants an additional %corruption_armor_pct_charge%%% armor reduction against the target.<br>Lose %death_lose_charge% energy points if killed by an enemy hero.\n<h1>Passive: Pierce</h1>Every attack has True Strike and deals %bonus_chance_damage% bonus magical damage.\nThis item is unique; all its attributes and effects are not stackable."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_cloud_razor_corruption"	"LACERATE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_cloud_razor_corruption_Description"	"Armor reduced by %fMODIFIER_PROPERTY_PHYSICAL_ARMOR_BONUS%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_blade_mail_Lore"		"<font color='#ffffff'>This is a <font color='#e80000'>Counter Spell</font>.</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thanksgiving_turkey"	"THANKSGIVING TURKEY"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_thanksgiving_turkey_Description"	"<h1>Active: Gobble Up</h1>Feast on the turkey to instantly level your hero up to level %UptoLevel%.\nThis turkey smells absolutely irresistible — you can't wait to dig in!<br>Best consumed before reaching level %UptoLevel%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_surprise_gift"	"HOLIDAY GIFT"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_surprise_gift_Description"	"<h1>Active: Open Gift</h1>Unwrap your gift to receive a random surprise!"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_revenants_brooch_Lore"		"<font color='#ffffff'><font color='#00BFFF'>Azure Sky Melody</font> and <font color='#00BFFF'>Star Chart</font> cannot increase this skill's damage.</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield"	"DARK SHIELD"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield_bonus_evasion"	"%+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_dark_shield_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Dark Mind</h1>For every %stack_threshold% physical damage before reductions that equipped hero receives, it gains a stack of Dark Mind for %stack_duration%s up to a maximum of %max_stacks% charges. Each charge increases this item's armor by %stack_armor%%% . \nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_shield_stack"	"DARK MIND"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_dark_shield_stack_Description"	"Armor increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP%."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power"	"FOULFELL POWER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_strength"	"+$str"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_lifesteal_percent"	"%+$lifesteal"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_bonus_evasion"	"%+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_foulfell_power_Description"	"<h1>Active: Unholy Rage</h1>Increases Lifesteal percentage to %unholy_lifesteal_percent%%% for %unholy_duration% seconds. <br><br>Dispel Type: <span class=\"GameplayValues GameplayVariable\">Basic Dispel</span> \n<h1>Passive: Lifesteal</h1>Heals the attacker for a percentage of attack damage dealt. Lifesteal from creeps is reduced by %creep_lifesteal_reduction_pct%%%. \n<h1>Passive: Shadow Wall</h1>Passively turns %heal_to_shield%%% of the overheal from this item to an all damage barrier up to %max_shield_hp% for %shield_duration% seconds. \n<h1>Passive: Dark Mind</h1>For every %stack_threshold% physical damage before reductions that equipped hero receives, it gains a stack of Dark Mind for %stack_duration%s up to a maximum of %max_stacks% charges. Each charge increases this item's armor by %stack_armor%%% . \nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable.\nFoulfell Power and Blood Sun can not work together. "
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power_shield"	"SHADOW WALL"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power_shield_Description"	"Absorbs damage."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power"				"UNHOLY RAGE"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_foulfell_power_Description"			"Lifesteal percentage increased."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3"	"BLOOD SUN"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_aoe"	"+$aoe_bonus"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_health"	"+$health"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_mana"	"+$mana"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_armor"	"+$armor"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_bonus_evasion"	"+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_spell_lifesteal"	"%+$spell_lifesteal"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_bloodstone_3_Description"    "<h1>Active: Bloodpact</h1>Increases this item's Spell Lifesteal to %lifesteal_multiplier%x and also converts the same percentage of damage dealt to mana. Lasts %buff_duration% seconds. \n<h1>Passive: Scarlet Barrier</h1>Passively turns %heal_to_shield%%% of the overheal from this item to an all damage barrier up to %max_shield_hp% for %shield_duration% seconds. \n<h1>Passive: Dark Mind</h1>For every %stack_threshold% physical damage before reductions that equipped hero receives, it gains a stack of Dark Mind for %stack_duration%s up to a maximum of %max_stacks% charges. Each charge increases this item's armor by %stack_armor%%% . \nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable.\nFoulfell Power and Blood Sun can not work together. "
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_shield"	"SCARLET BARRIER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_shield_Description"	"Absorbs damage."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3"	"BLOODPACT"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_Description"	"Spell Lifesteal percentage increased."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_drained"	"DRAINED"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_bloodstone_3_drained_Description"	"Bloodpact's Bonuses will not apply to a unit that's drained."

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2"	"MORPHO"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_agi"	"+$agi"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_attack_speed"	"+$attack"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_evasion"	"+$evasion"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_bonus_damage"	"+$damage"
"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_butterfly_2_Description"	"<h1>Passive: Riddle of Wind</h1>Attack speed increased by %bonus_attack_speed_pct%%%, Agility increased by %bonus_agi_pct%%%. <br><br>For every %bonus_attack_speed_limit_threshold% agility of equipped heroes, the maximum attack speed increased by %bonus_attack_speed_limit% and the maximum by %bonus_attack_speed_limit_max%. \n<h1>Passive: Flutter</h1>Every attack grants %buff_attack_speed% attack speed for %buff_duration% seconds, stacking up to %buff_max_stack% times. At maximum stacks, grants extra %buff_attack_speed_max_stack% attack speed and %buff_agi_max_stack% agility. \nThis item is unique, all its attributes and effects are not stackable."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2"	"RIDDLE OF WIND"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2_Description"	"Maximum attack speed increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP% (up to %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_TOOLTIP2%)."
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2_buff_damage"	"FLUTTER"
"DOTA_Tooltip_modifier_item_butterfly_2_buff_damage_Description"	"Attack speed increased by %dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_ATTACKSPEED_BONUS_CONSTANT%, agility increased by%dMODIFIER_PROPERTY_STATS_AGILITY_BONUS%. "

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_chipped_vest_Lore"		"<font color='#ffffff'>This is a <font color='#e80000'>Counter Spell</font>.</font>"

"DOTA_Tooltip_ability_item_force_field_Lore"		"<font color='#ffffff'>This is a <font color='#e80000'>Counter Spell</font>.</font>"
	}
}